title: Unique, Quaint, Custom Upgrades, In The Heart of Downtown Chanhassen!
posting_body: ['Contact info:', 'Mike Miller | The Apartment Resource |', 'show contact info', '2Br/2Ba - Walking Distance to Shopping, Dining and Parks!', 'W 78th St, Chanhassen, MN 55317', '$1,720/month', 'KEY FEATURES', 'Sq Footage:', '1000 sqft.', 'Bedrooms:', '2', 'Bathrooms:', '2', 'Parking:', '2 Dedicated', 'Lease Duration:', '12 Months', 'Deposit:', '$500', 'Pets Policy:', 'Cats & Dogs OK', 'Laundry:', 'In Unit', 'Property Type:', 'Apartment', 'DESCRIPTION', 'This outstanding apartment community is located in Downtown Chanhassen, featuring 1, 1 plus den and 2 bedroom, dog and cat friendly apartments for rent.', 'You are sure to fall in love with these open and airy homes, each with a balcony or patio, generous closet space, and a washer and dryer in your home.', 'Take a stroll to fine dining at Axels, or walk to the Chanhassen Dinner Theater for a fine night of entertainment, or spend a day of relaxation at Spalon Montage.', 'Walking distance to parks, Chanhassen Library and grocery shopping, Equal Housing Opportunity.', 'Prices and availability are subject to change.', 'Photos may not represent exact unit.', 'COMMUNITY AMENITIES', 'In-Unit Washer/Dryer', 'Elevator in Building', 'Controlled Building Access', 'Community Room', 'Soft water included', 'Close to Shopping, Restaurants and Downtown', 'Weekly coffee hour', 'Car wash', 'Trash chutes/recycling', 'Cable Ready', 'Located in Residential Neighborhood', '24-Hour Emergency Maintenance', 'BBQ Grilling Area', 'On Site Management Office', 'Balcony/Patio', 'High Speed Internet Available', 'Fitness Center', 'Heated Underground Parking', 'Pets Welcome!', 'Contact info:', 'Mike Miller', 'The Apartment Resource', 'show contact info']
